Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.79,0:28:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings from the boys\Ndown at the miII?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.40,0:28:47.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但先来点音乐.
