Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.85,0:28:51.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好, 本杰明.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.14,0:28:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Benjamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.20,0:28:56.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 很抱歉我没有\N亲自去探望你, 亲爱的.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.48,0:28:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, l'm sorry l haven't\Ndropped by for a visit, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.73,0:29:00.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我非常厌恶\N去监狱.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.02,0:29:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l have a strong aversion\Nto prisons.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.83,0:29:03.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那里太恶心了--\N- 她还活着?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.09,0:29:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- How awful--\N- She's aIive?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.92,0:29:09.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们共度的那晚\N迷失在爱意里.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.19,0:29:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The night we spent together\Nlost in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.41,0:29:14.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那时什么时候的事了?\N似乎那么的遥远.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.66,0:29:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When was that?\Nlt seems so long ago.
