Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.50,0:29:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.56,0:29:22.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 对, 我记起来了,\N就是劳拉·帕尔默死的那晚.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.80,0:29:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, l remember,\Nit was the night Laura Palmer died.
