Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.87,0:29:46.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你要把锯木厂\N和格斯伍的地产合同签回来给我.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.13,0:29:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will sign the mill and\NGhostwood Estates back over to me.
