Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.92,0:39:36.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,女士们, 快去快回.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.19,0:39:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies, hurry back.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.70,0:39:56.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都不会说的,\N对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.97,0:39:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna say anything,\Nare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.23,0:40:00.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果维维安发现\N我在里面呆过,她会--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.48,0:40:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Vivian ever found out\NI'd been inside she'd--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.24,0:40:01.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她会把我扔下公寓的.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.51,0:40:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd drop me fIat.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.54,0:40:03.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你的新发色.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.81,0:40:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Iike your new hair coIor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.25,0:40:08.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,尔尼·奈尔斯.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.48,0:40:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ernie NiIes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.30,0:40:10.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,尔尼·奈尔斯教授.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.55,0:40:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ernie ''The Professor'' NiIes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.13,0:40:14.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那你是什么时候?\N- 2周前.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.39,0:40:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- So when did you?\N- A coupIe of weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.66,0:40:16.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,让我告诉你吧, 尔尼,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.89,0:40:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me teII you, Ernie,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.31,0:40:20.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有你在的最后6个月里\N那里简直糟透了.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.56,0:40:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without you in there to paI around with\Nthe Iast six months were sheer heII.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.28,0:40:21.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再也没人去图书馆.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.57,0:40:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody to go to the Iibrary with.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.20,0:40:25.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也没人轧制\N车牌了.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.47,0:40:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody to stamp out\NIicense pIates with.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.20,0:40:29.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么, 你钓这富婆\N来这儿干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.47,0:40:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's your angIe here\Nwith Miss Moneybags?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.26,0:40:31.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不钓了.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.51,0:40:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No angIe.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.78,0:40:33.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,少来了, 兄弟,\N我们之间还有什么秘密.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.04,0:40:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, buddy,\Nwe don't have any secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.96,0:40:35.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,维维安可是在钱堆儿里打滚的人.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.25,0:40:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivian's roIIing in dough.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.36,0:40:39.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在共和党筹款会上\N认识维维安的.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.61,0:40:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met Vivian\Nat a RepubIican fundraiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.71,0:40:41.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们结婚了.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.98,0:40:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're married.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.59,0:40:45.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定跟她讲了\N什么大话, 漫天大谎.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.85,0:40:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have toId her\Nsome taII taIe, a whopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.85,0:40:48.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我最近试着不讲大话了\N除了真相外.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.12,0:40:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying very hard to teII nothing\Nbut the truth these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.04,0:40:51.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是一种治疗.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.29,0:40:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's therapeutic.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.35,0:40:57.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,维维安想我着手操作\N她所有的投资.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.60,0:40:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Vivian wants me to handIe\NaII her investments.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.66,0:41:01.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么你的呢?\N介绍她认识你的高利贷主吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.94,0:41:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about yours?\NIntroduce her to your Ioan shark?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.67,0:41:05.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我戒了, 我戒了, 汉克.\N我不再赌了.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.94,0:41:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out of it, I'm out of it, Hank.\NI don't gambIe anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.98,0:41:09.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我去参加聚会. 还去教堂.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.24,0:41:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I go to meetings. I go to church too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.34,0:41:11.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么, 维维安发现你\N拿了教会的野餐基金跑路了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.61,0:41:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what happens when\NVivian finds out that you ran off
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.82,0:41:15.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 会怎么样呢?\N- 我从没在教堂偷过东西.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.08,0:41:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- with the congregation's picnic fund?\N- I never stoIe from a church.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.79,0:41:18.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我有存款还有些贷款.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.05,0:41:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a savings and Ioan.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.79,0:41:20.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我生病了, 得了一种疾病.\N后来还清了债务.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.06,0:41:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sick, it was an iIIness.\NI paid my debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.02,0:41:24.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是新生活, 清白的-- 改头换面了.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.26,0:41:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a new Iife, a cIean-- CIean sIate.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.98,0:41:29.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那么她真的不知道咯?\N- 不知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.23,0:41:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- So she reaIIy doesn't know?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.86,0:41:32.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 尔尼, 这我倒感兴趣了.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.13,0:41:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WeII, Ernie, this is interesting to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.48,0:41:37.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因为家对我来说\N是这世界上最重要的.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.74,0:41:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because famiIy is the most\Nimportant thing in the worId to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.57,0:41:41.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人一定要准备着\N不惜一切代价去保护它.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.84,0:41:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One must be prepared\Nto pay any price to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.15,0:41:43.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你能不同意吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.41,0:41:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.16,0:41:48.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 是, 是. 我完全同意.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.42,0:41:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, yeah. I compIeteIy agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.03,0:41:51.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们回头再仔细聊, 尔尼.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.29,0:41:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'II taIk more Iater, Ernie.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.91,0:41:54.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢\N在花园里聊天,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.16,0:41:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've aIways enjoyed\Nour taIks in the yard,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.17,0:41:56.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,男人对男人, 囚犯对囚犯.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.43,0:41:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,man-to-man, prisoner-to-prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.09,0:42:00.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们回来了.\N- 女士们.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.36,0:42:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- We're back.\N- Ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.50,0:42:08.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们来举杯庆祝一下
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.80,0:42:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouId Iike to propose a toast
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.29,0:42:11.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,祝新婚夫妇\N幸福快乐.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.57,0:42:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the newIyweds\Nand their happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.82,0:42:14.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你, 小汉克.\N太有风度了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.08,0:42:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Henry.\NIt's very generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.17,0:42:16.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,祝尔尼和维维安,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.45,0:42:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Ernie and Vivian,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.01,0:42:22.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,祝他们的未来和事业\N更加成功.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.28,0:42:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to much success in their future\Nand aII their future deaIings.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.58,0:42:24.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,太动听了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.82,0:42:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.72,0:42:26.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,太动人了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.99,0:42:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.48,0:43:01.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,戴安, 晚上11:05. 我在\N北方大酒店的房间里.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.72,0:43:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diane, it's 1 1 :05 p.m. I'm in my room\Nat the Great Northern HoteI.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.06,0:43:04.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚天上没有一颗星星.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.33,0:43:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not a star in the sky tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.11,0:43:07.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本·荷恩在拘留所.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.36,0:43:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben Horne is in custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.42,0:43:09.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,范围收窄了, 戴安.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.67,0:43:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The traiI narrows, Diane.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.16,0:43:11.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我离答案很近了,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.40,0:43:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very cIose,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.43,0:43:15.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但最后几步总是\N最黑暗最难的.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.67,0:43:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the Iast few steps are aIways\Nthe darkest and most difficuIt.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.78,0:43:35.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨.\N- 欧蕊?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.03,0:43:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hi.\N- Audrey?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.00,0:43:39.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我能进来来聊聊吗?\N- 好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.26,0:43:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Can I come in and taIk?\N- AII right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.71,0:43:44.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你就是那里中枪了?\N- 是啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.97,0:43:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Is that where you got shot?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.42,0:43:48.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你逮捕他了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.67,0:43:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you arrest him?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.34,0:43:52.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.61,0:43:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.13,0:43:55.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是他干的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.38,0:43:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.17,0:43:58.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那留给法庭去裁定吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.45,0:43:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for a court to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.79,0:44:00.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.05,0:44:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.27,0:44:03.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么\N现在已经不重要了.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.55,0:44:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I think\Ndoesn't reaIIy matter right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.15,0:44:06.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你逮捕他\N是因为我所说的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.42,0:44:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you arrest him\Nbecause of what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.98,0:44:08.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,部分吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.22,0:44:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OnIy in part.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.03,0:44:10.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但有帮助?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.29,0:44:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it heIped?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.60,0:44:12.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.83,0:44:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.82,0:44:18.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾想要的所有\N不过是希望他爱我.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.07,0:44:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AII I ever reaIIy wanted\Nwas for him to Iove me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.96,0:44:21.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定他是爱你的.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.20,0:44:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.19,0:44:24.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他为我感到羞耻.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.47,0:44:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's ashamed of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.15,0:44:26.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 他不是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.44,0:44:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.69,0:44:36.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀探员,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.95,0:44:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Cooper,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.39,0:44:41.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我在单眼杰克赌场时,\N我从没有, 从没有被任何人--
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.66,0:44:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I was at One-Eyed Jack's,\NI never, never Iet anyone--
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.05,0:44:45.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊, 你什么\N都不必说了.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.33,0:44:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey, you don't have\Nto say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.37,0:44:46.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我想让你知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.60,0:44:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.07,0:44:48.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.33,0:44:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.87,0:44:58.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要接电话了.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.11,0:44:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.27,0:45:00.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.54,0:45:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.50,0:45:10.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是库珀. 在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.79,0:45:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooper here. Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.82,0:45:14.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,多久之前的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.06,0:45:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How Iong ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.99,0:45:17.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我马上就到.\N- 出什么事啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.26,0:45:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm on my way.\N- What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.05,0:45:19.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你回自己房间\N把门锁好.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.30,0:45:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to go to your room\Nand Iock the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.14,0:45:23.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 为什么?\N- 别问了, 照我说的做.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.40,0:45:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why?\N- No questions, do what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.32,0:45:25.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.57,0:45:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AII right.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.34,0:46:14.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是马蒂·弗格逊.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.62,0:46:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Maddy Ferguson.
